Porto Says No Deal Done to Release Coach Amid Report He’ll Join Chelsea

-- B y   A l e x   D u f f
-- 
2011-06-20T12:22:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-20/porto-says-no-deal-done-to-release-coach-amid-report-he-ll-join-chelsea.html
Porto said it hasn’t received
notification that coach Andre Villas-Boas is going to be
released from his contract, according to a statement to
 Portugal ’s stock-market regulator.  Earlier today, the Lusa news agency reported Premier League
runner-up Chelsea agreed to pay the Portuguese soccer champion
15 million euros ($21.4 million) to hire Villas-Boas.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
